{"tid":37112,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"諗返起早幾年被人笑 IVE 仔","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T20:27:35.000Z","uid":14170,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b361235ac46b91e8fc57d5bc1978065e921180","tid":37112,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:58:33.000Z","msg":"有次同老母行街撞到個幾年無見既姨姨同佢仔仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家見面就實寒暄幾句，問下仲有無繼續讀書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姨：咦你讀 IVE 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個仔今年入左理大喎，見佢晚晚讀書都覺得辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：係呀聽講讀大學好辛苦（我爆四都好辛苦，不過廢是拎出黎被人笑啦）<br />\n<br />\n然後佢一路係度講佢個仔點點點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我老母忍唔住，話我啱啱收到中大 Offer，下年入學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個姨姨就無再提個仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c544168d79f56645dd562d9a36fcb918cd5af44","tid":37112,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"最近又撞返佢，佢再問我邊度讀書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我再更新返係港大，佢就再無提過自己個仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時覺得呢啲師奶心態真係好 on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有風駛盡艃，講野做人唔留情面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd20c4c850e09719875e558c484672150918942","tid":37112,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"我諗我老母都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba865a51c26108ec13cae0e69d84062abc9fe313","ti